snippet.title: Game Boy Advance Longplay [071] Need for Speed: Underground
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Stenio_Henrique

Enter the world of street racing with Need For Speed Underground. Go to Underground Mode to challenge other racers, earn money and buy parts for your car and become the best pilot in the city.

The look of my cars were inspired by : Mitsubishi Eclipse 1995 ( Brian ) , Nissan Skyline R33 (Leon) , Mazda RX-7 (Toretto's). I'ma big fan of fast and furious and this is an awesome game.

The Soundtrack is : Lil Jon - Get Low , Static X - The Only , Overseer - Doomsday , Jerk - Sucked In.

Now I leave a quote from Dominic Toretto : "Ask any racer, any real racer. It doesn't matter if you win by an inch or a mile; winning's winning." -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
